+ Abstraction

      o Draw a Cat
      o Draw a Dog

Java Lists

+ The most common of List, Set, Map
   - Arrays are common as well.
+ A Collection of some Object
   - Not a collection of primitive
+ Can have duplicates in the list
+ Ordered by how you (or how DB) puts things into the List
+ Often times we get a List back from the Database
   - How do I go through all the elements of a list?
   - How do I filter a list?
+ Abstract: List
+ Concrete: Array List, Linked List
   - Under-The-Hood details of these two
   - Pro's and Con's of Array vs Linked
+ We get an element by index.
